![Episode11.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1575061963016-LGVX080CTSJDBLBPPNID/Episode11.jpg)

Happy Valentine's Day to everyone in comic book land! On this special love-filled episode the guys at ComicBook Clique dicuss romance in comics and debate over the best couple in comic history! Nothing is off the table as they narrow down their picks for best kiss between comic characters, and ponder what's the most romantic moment in comic history! Feel the LOVE!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

